title: Received "liquid or debris in usb port" message 5 hours ago. The phone won't charge and is now dead
content: I got a "liquid or debris in usb port" message about 5 hours ago. The message states the phone automatically disables the port.   I can't see anything in the port. I waited a couple of hours then clicked on enable usb but it will not charge. How do I get the usb port to be enabled again?
